The '''Aldera Museum of Modern Expression''' was an art museum on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]], presumably in or near [[Aldera/Legends|Aldera]]. It's "sister" museum was the [[Tantive Gallery of Progressive Art]] on [[Tantive IV (planet)|Tantive IV]].

